00:37:57.914 --> 00:38:03.652
Svilom... i s mojih 12 funti.

00:38:15.863 --> 00:38:17.662
Znači, to je to?

00:38:19.965 --> 00:38:21.900
Slobodan si.

00:39:05.557 --> 00:39:06.858
Dobro.

00:39:21.403 --> 00:39:23.937
Robeson, tu sam!

00:39:23.971 --> 00:39:25.905
Robeson, trebam pomoć!

00:39:56.110 --> 00:39:59.147
Evo ga!
